<article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article" id="article-body" section="articleBody"><meta itemprop="thumbnailUrl" content="http://cnet3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2013/11/27/4fa1e84a-67d7-11e3-a665-14feb5ca9861/thumbnail/770x433/598c41bc7e36502d92d8d02dd1bbda5e/Ray_Ozzie_PDC.jpg"><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Tech Industry, Phones, Mobile"><meta itemprop="url" content="http://www.cnet.com/news/steve-ballmers-replacement-needs-to-make-this-phone-call/"><h1 itemprop="headline">Steve Ballmer's replacement needs to make this phone call</h1>
        <p class="article-dek" itemprop="description">If Microsoft's outgoing chief executive had listened to Ray Ozzie, Microsoft's incoming CEO would have a much easier go of it.</p>
    
            
    <div id="article-info" class="row article-byline" section="author">
        <ul><li itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">by
                                                            <a itemprop="name" rel="author" class="author" href="http://www.cnet.com/profiles/charlie+cooper/">
                            Charles Cooper
                        </a>
                    
                                            <span class="asset-twitter">
                            <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=coopeydoop" class="twitter-follow-link">
                                <div class="twitter">
                                    <div class="icon icon-twitter-red"></div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                                                            <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=coopeydoop" class="twitter-follow-link">@coopeydoop</a>
                                                    </span>
                    
                                                                    </li>

                                                        <li><time itemprop="datePublished" class="2013-11-27 11:00:00">November 27, 2013 3:00 AM PST</time></li>
            
                                </ul></div>
    
            

    
    
<ul class="sharebar inline-view" data-component="sharebar" data-sharebar-options='{"title":"Steve Ballmer\u0027s replacement needs to make this phone call","description":"If Microsoft\u0027s outgoing chief executive had listened to Ray Ozzie, Microsoft\u0027s incoming CEO would have a much easier go of it.","url":"http:\/\/www.cnet.com\/news\/steve-ballmers-replacement-needs-to-make-this-phone-call\/","data":{"media":"http:\/\/cnet4.cbsistatic.com\/hub\/i\/r\/2013\/11\/27\/4fa1e84a-67d7-11e3-a665-14feb5ca9861\/thumbnail\/170x128\/070f05daa3fe1ead059419b4768a731e\/Ray_Ozzie_PDC.jpg"}}'><li class="comment-count" data-livefyre-count="4f99b342-67d7-11e3-a665-14feb5ca9861">
